  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0da2\u0db6\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajaben proposes Sajitwa for the presidency",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today (11) the group of MPs of Samagi Jana Balawega unanimously decided to propose the opposition leader Mr. Sajith Premadasa for the post of President.",
        "The resolution was brought by the General Secretary of the party Mr. Ranjith Maddumabandara.",
        "The MP group meeting of Samagi Jana Balawega and Samagi Jana Sandanha was held this afternoon at the office of the opposition leader in Marx Fernando Mawatha, Colombo.",
        "Party General Secretary Ranjith Madduma Bandara said that if President Gotabaya Rajapaksa resigns tomorrow (13), Mr. Sajith Pemadasa will be nominated for the post of President."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Sajaben",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
